title: Slade - Keep Your Hands Off My Power Supply (1984)
description:
From Wikipedia:

Keep Your Hands Off My Power Supply is an album by the British glam/hardrock group Slade. This was an alternate version of The Amazing Kamikaze Syndrome which was released in the UK. It was released in the U.S. in 1984 and reached number 33 in the US charts.

This album proved to be Slade's most successful American album despite over 20 years of releases in the States. Both "Run Runaway" and "My Oh My" continue to receive consistent radio airplay in the United States and are their most recognizable songs amongst Americans.
